# REQ-AXO-902024 — generated SOLL export dumps: dense in SOLL ids (thousands of
# phantom matches), pure regenerable artefacts with no source value. The dense
# docs/vision/ ones are already gitignored; this class-level rule also keeps the
# indexer off the tracked tiny docs/archive/soll-exports/ history and any future
# export location. The A+B+C chunker fixes make them non-wedging regardless; this
# just avoids spending any pipeline time on a zero-value generated dump.
**/SOLL_EXPORT_*.md
